#: ../../library/functions.rst:1455
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When reading input from the stream, if *newline* is ``None``, universal "
"newlines mode is enabled.  Lines in the input can end in ``'\\n'``, "
"``'\\r'``, or ``'\\r\\n'``, and these are translated into ``'\\n'`` before "
